codex
A key finding already: H1 does not call `snapToCellFloor()` inside each segment in the current code. 
That call is after the segment loop, so the proposal’s side-effect list needs correction there; the 
per-segment side effects are collision resolution, obstacle list rebuild/sweep, terrain handling, 
and `storePosition()`.
