codex
There’s also a subtle H2-only hazard: `findFirstContact()` chooses the earliest contact across both 
extents and floor contacts by comparing `contact.m_time` directly. A floor-only substep must return 
a full-segment normalized time, or it will change ordering against static/dynamic extents.
